      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAXON KELTON (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (24.84) in a Grade 5 at Sale. Form here sound including three wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings six times from eight starts. Has ability and can bounce back. SPECIAL SIAN (6) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (19.92) at this track behind Sailplane in a Grade 5. Expected to be in this for a long way. ELLA AUDACIOUS (7) last start finished 3rd over 300m at this track beaten 2.75 lengths (17.13) behind Happy Chick in a Grade 5 on April 3. Suited here and expected to run well. RED HOT PRETTY (2) cannot be underestimated.",
